{"tid":2311183,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"皇后大道東","createTime":"2020-12-04T00:54:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T01:35:37.000Z","uid":172982,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9f58dc27b9ddae48391424dbedf74db8e053e6aa","tid":2311183,"uid":172982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T00:54:28.000Z","msg":"利申 80後<br />\n<br />\n細個果陣聽呢首歌覺得好膠 羅大佑把聲又沙沙地 廣東話又唔係好正 點解當年會爆紅？<br />\n<br />\n今日再細心聽返呢首歌 發現由配樂 歌詞都係一流之作<br />\n<br />\n今日去填呢d歌詞會唔會踩到紅線？<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;有個貴族朋友在硬幣背後 青春不變名字叫做皇后&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時會禁埋女皇頭既硬幣？"},{"pid":"a64363c48844a599f157b0d9b1ba2ae633c10e17","tid":2311183,"uid":172982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T01:35:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}